product_description.FM Radio and MP3 Player: While its MP3 player helps you listen to your favourite tracks, its wireless FM radio keeps you updated with the latest news and tracks even when you’re on the move. Also, the dual-faced speakers and dedicated music buttons enhance your entertainment experience.
product_description.Design: With its smooth curves, easy-to-use buttons and a comfortable grip, this phone’s classic design makes it all the more convenient.
product_description.Designed for Music Lovers: Its clear, curved display helps you view the screen to see what’s playing quickly. Also, the dedicated music buttons help you change the tracks with ease.
product_description.Battery: Its long-lasting battery keeps you entertained for long hours after a single, full charge. It runs for days in the standby mode and for hours when you’re on a call.
